Japan, Iwate, Morioka, Ueda, Campus of Iwate University, on dead culms of 
<taxonomicName id="C39A90A93F9BB0E50E4EAD6579AFCDFC" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Phyllostachys" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Phyllostachys pubescens" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="147" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pubescens">
